data.description: PRICE REDUCTION UNDER APPRASIAL VALUE** WELCOME HOME to this beautifully maintained home in sought after Senoia. Don't miss out on this 3 bedroom/2 bath ranch home because it won't last long. Once you walk in the door you will find a large living room with custom built-in bookcases. It has an open concept design with a view of living room, dining room and kitchen. It has a new roof installed in the last 3 months. This property is located within minutes from downtown Senioa, shopping, and the interstate.
